Simple two pointer approach 
1. convert the string in char array both string
2.useing the for loop 
  1. get char of the both string 
  2. if char equal then contine
  3. if char not equal
    1. using the function getindex to find the index of char in s1 string 
  4. and find the diff and diff equal 2 then swap the character
  5. if diff not equal 2 then return false
3. check both string is equal return true otherwise false;
  
